# Day 41 – Interactive Learning Studio using Claude AI

## 📌 Objective

The objective of this project was to build an interactive learning platform that teaches a complete topic through structured modules, quizzes, practical exercises, and a final challenge. The application provides a guided learning experience while tracking user progress.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Interactive Learning Modules
- Step-by-Step Topic Explanations
- Practical Examples & Exercises
- Interactive Quizzes with Instant Feedback
- Automatic Quiz Scoring
- Progress Tracking
- Final Practical Challenge
- Cheat Sheet & Summary Notes
- Learning Resources
- Responsive Dark Mode UI
- Offline Support

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript

